		<item>
		<title>No Nessus gui client and limited support of the server for openSUSE</title>
		<link>/blog-archive/2009/09/02/no-nessus-gui-client-and-limited-support-of-the-server-for-opensuse.html</link>
		<comments>/blog-archive/2009/09/02/no-nessus-gui-client-and-limited-support-of-the-server-for-opensuse.html#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 02 Sep 2009 13:27:36 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[phocean]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Linux]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Pentesting]]></category>
